{"tid":2306282,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK疑被馬來西亞女團Dolla抄襲　齊瀏海成員更撞樣Lisa？","createTime":"2020-11-30T10:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:25:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9142e4f8c314dd7929496094a94d5ee506f187d5","tid":2306282,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:21:22.000Z","msg":"韓國女團BLAKCPINK擁全球性高人氣，海內外都有不少歌手視她們為偶像。近日，去年9月出道的馬來西亞女團Dolla被指不論風格及造型有抄襲BLACKPINK之嫌，其中剪了齊瀏海的成員更撞樣Lisa。<br />\n<br />\nDolla去年9月出道，今年一首《Dolla Make You Wanna》成功打響知名度。可是人紅自然是非多，有眼利網友發現Dolla爆紅後的風格等，都與BLACKPINK非常相似，其中黑粉紅色配色的海報設計最為明顯。而Dolla 4位成員的造型亦與初出道非常不同，當中剪了齊瀏海的成員更被指撞樣Lisa，Jennie、Jisoo和Ros&eacute;等的影子亦隱約在其他成員身上看到。<br />\n<br />\n面對抄襲BLACKPINK的質疑，Dolla官方有出面回應澄清沒有任何抄襲意圖；而成員Sabronzo也講到，雖然大眾覺得組合在抄襲，但Dolla仍有屬於自己的風格，相似的地方只是巧合。Dolla亦講到自己是BLACKPINK的粉絲，她們亦拍攝了《How You Like That》翻跳影片致敬偶像。可是影片卻惹來更多不滿，被BLACKPINK粉絲大鬧「請不要再消費他人做宣傳」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201130/410072758433615872521476.jpeg/hGDYCKci_OY80al7SO1NjOyQkr6-poQyLo4faC6OH2g?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201130%2F410072758433615872521476.jpeg%2FhGDYCKci_OY80al7SO1NjOyQkr6-poQyLo4faC6OH2g%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c8309b1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"738646c11eac999fb100556bbc1023d4f84b985f","tid":2306282,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201130/410074261756186624479850.jpeg/cXIvpQvffwqWpVDy63e4NuFu8iSvZJERXpix-V6Ysfk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201130%2F410074261756186624479850.jpeg%2FcXIvpQvffwqWpVDy63e4NuFu8iSvZJERXpix-V6Ysfk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e9d32d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201130/410074264189014016504291.jpeg/tPZIn7XoHOXq2LEAl-PX5UzdN0SVd0aMBX34bAV9-Gw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-sr